Components.Label: Search
Components.Query:
select Shipment.Id as Id,
pol.Name as polName,
pod.Name as podName,
pt.Name as ptName,
(select top 1 concat(format(EtaTsDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'/',format(EtdTsDate,'yyyy-MM-dd')) from EntityTransit where EntityId = Shipment.ParentId and PortTransitId = Shipment.PortTransitId) as etaTsDate
from Shipment
left join Terminal pol on Shipment.POLId = pol.Id
left join Terminal pod on Shipment.PODId = pod.Id
left join Terminal pt on Shipment.PortTransitId = pt.Id
where (Shipment.HblNo = '{SearchNo}' or Shipment.BookingNo = '{SearchNo}') and Shipment.CustomerId = '{TokenUserId}'
